[[File:GreyshadeSpeeder-HNNv531no56.png|thumb|right|150px|The engine, as used in the [[XJ-6 airspeeder/Legends|XJ-6 airspeeder]] as a dual set.]]
This '''engine''' was a type of engine used in seventh-stage bank-courier [[Seventh-stage bank-courier repulsor-truck/Legends|repulsor-trucks]], which were common on the [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Aargau/Legends|Aargau]]. The [[XJ-6 airspeeder/Legends|XJ-6]] utilized this type of engine, which, due to its use in larger cargo-carrying [[Airspeeder/Legends|airspeeders]], could produce a great deal more speed and power in a smaller, sportier type of craft.

